# Allowlist for Felt differential tests.
# Format: "from-literal" -> "to-literal"     (fixed-string substitution; comments after are free-form)
# See harness/differential.md §2 (Allowlist) and harness/coverage.md §Attributes.

# VEIR stores felt.const's value as IntegerAttr; LLZK as #felt.const<N>.
# Collapse to the LLZK form before diff. (harness/coverage.md §Attributes:#felt.const)
"<{value = 42 : i256}>" -> "<{value = #felt.const<42>}>"
"<{value = 7 : i256}>" -> "<{value = #felt.const<7>}>"
